    "description": "Join the MyGlamm Global Group family as a Marketplace Manager in Hyderabad. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout MyGlamm Global Group:\nMyGlamm Global Group is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Hyderabad, Telangana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with MyGlamm Global Group!",
